            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">5</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            He took the punishment for sin upon himself so that we may enjoy peace. By his wounds we are healed. On the third day, He rose again from the dead and ascended into heaven and is seated at the right hand of God the Father, and will return to judge the world.
          </p>
        </div>
        
